{"tid":1463503,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"眼球中彈女子身份是急救員！ 網怒轟港警違《國際人道法》","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:22:13.000Z","uid":41998,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3c59ae953fac89357d6b6285119bf7ba523defdd","tid":1463503,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:13:10.000Z","msg":"香港「反送中」抗爭昨（11）日遭香港警方空前強勢鎮壓，一名示威女子遭射爆右眼，據傳已造成永久性失明，引發示威民眾憤慨，有香港網友號召百萬人在今（12）日塞爆機場，為女子討回雙眼。而根據「美版PTT」Reddit的帳號名稱「r／Hong Kong」張貼訊息指出，該名女子身份為一名第一線急救員，引起網友震驚並熱議。<br />\n<br />\n反送中昨日下午兵分兩路遊行，但警方事先並未批准，遊行因此再度演變為遍地開花的游擊戰，遭到警方全面升級強勢鎮壓，而且近距離對示威者發射橡膠子彈、布袋彈與胡椒彈；其中一名黑衣女子臉部遭疑似布袋彈擊中，右眼血流不止，被緊急送往醫院接受急救手術。<br />\n<br />\n今日有一位網友自稱受傷女子的妹妹發文，表示該女子右眼全紫，腫成約雞蛋大小，右眼眼頭至眼袋有長型傷口，鼻骨、眉骨碎裂，做了緊急手術，但因有碎骨，「一定會毀容」。因此有香港網友發起「警察還眼」行動塞爆香港國際機場，更有醫護人員靜坐抗議譴責警方濫暴行為。<br />\n<br />\n而根據「美版PTT」Reddit的「r／Hong Kong」張貼訊息指出，該名女子身份為一名第一線急救員，引起網友震驚，而且多數網友留言指出香港警察違反日內瓦公約中的《國際人道法》。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">《國際人道法》指出，就算爆發戰爭，也應避免對平民、難民、受傷或生病的士兵、戰俘、記者、醫護人員、宗教人士等進行攻擊，然而這條法不具備國際法律文件的效力，但也被當成是促進注重人權、人道的重要準則。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ftvnews.com.tw/news/detail/2019812W0020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftvnews.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F2019812W0020&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BmWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=10cd8637\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ftvnews.com.tw/news/detail/2019812W0020</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EjZJ0TB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEjZJ0TB.jpg&h=6a5635e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[緊急][更新] 我係爆眼女first aids個妹，想再同大家講啲野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1454291/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1454291/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n甚麼是國際人道法？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.redcross.org.hk/tc/rcmovement/ihl.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redcross.org.hk%2Ftc%2Frcmovement%2Fihl.html&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BmWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=fca37c40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.redcross.org.hk/tc/rcmovement/ihl.html</a>"},{"pid":"8e54e0777892b3ff219a2e4cfcddd28cc134a128","tid":1463503,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:14:15.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"a980a70ca9d8f9d777c02a1556201cf099c559ee","tid":1463503,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:15:34.000Z","msg":"821夜晚荃灣仲有休班警圍嘔準備番屋企既fa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725922ec9eaad94e91569104fa773f739cdb4fbc","tid":1463503,"uid":41998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:20:01.000Z","msg":"我發覺香港有啲新聞仲用緊「示威者」嚟形容佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔撚係啊! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係急救員!佢係急救員!佢係急救員!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded02e5d8792f0073bf0deb497ae6bceeb53e191","tid":1463503,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:25:36.000Z","msg":"She was a first-aider<br />\nShe was a first-aider<br />\nShe was a first-aider<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">The women whose eyes were shot was a first-aider. The Hong Kong police has now broken the Geneva Convention.</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0f9359718731138adb32656b5d4474f777b28b45","tid":1463503,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:37:33.000Z","msg":"She was a first-aider<br />\nShe was a fi