 />\n<a href=\"https://www.icrc.org/en/document/what-international-humanitarian-law\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icrc.org%2Fen%2Fdocument%2Fwhat-international-humanitarian-law&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BmWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=8e100d8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.icrc.org/en/document/what-international-humanitarian-law</a><br />\n<br />\n利申：自己有份喺香城online做醫療兵，上面講咗只係想文宣準確啲"}]}